txt.en: 'Very good, [placeholder]! That ought to keep them away from those folk for a bit!'

Nedda Pinleaf has asked you to seek out Harbingers of the Dead near the Strongholds of the Free Peoples.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>NOTE: Harbingers of the Dead can be found in the following skirmishes: Defence of The Prancing Pony, Thievery and Mischief, Trouble in Tuckborough, Siege of Gondamon, Stand at Amon Sûl, and Doom of Caras Gelebren. You only need to complete four of the six listed quests today to advance this quest.</rgb>

Harbingers of the Dead are assaulting the strongholds of the Free Peoples of Middle-earth.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>NOTE: This quest will be removed from your quest log when the event it is associated with ends.</rgb>
Skirmish Assault: Strongholds of the Free Peoples
Complete 'Ill Omens: Defence of The Prancing Pony'

'[placeholder]!

'I've heard tell that the Harbingers of the Dead have been spotted near several of the strongholds of the Free Peoples.

'Let's get out there and stop them!'
Nedda Pinleaf can be found at the skirmish camps of Bree, Ost Galadh, and the Twenty-first Hall.\n\nYou should talk to Nedda Pinleaf.
<rgb=#8373ff>A Harbinger of the Dead has appeared!</rgb>
Complete 'Ill Omens: Stand at Amon Sûl'
Complete 'Ill Omens: Doom of Caras Gelebren'
